gems.name: google-local-results-ai-parser
gems.info: A gem to be used with serpapi/bert-base-local-results model to predict different parts of Google Local Listings. This gem uses BERT model at https://huggingface.co/serpapi/bert-base-local-results in the background. For serving private servers, head to https://github.com/serpapi/google-local-results-ai-server to get more information.
